						</cfif>

						<br/>

						<cfif arguments.action NEQ "delete"><!---Si el elemento no se elimina--->
							<!---<div style="border-color:##CCCCCC; color:##666666; border-style:solid; border-width:1px; padding:8px;">#access_content#</div>--->

